
============================================================================

     hamc  =  Hall  A  Monte  Carlo

     R. Michaels,  Nov 2008

============================================================================

To proceed do the following

Compile:

    make clean
    make

Run

    ./hamc
   (and don't forget the dot "." and slash "/")

Histogram output

    hamc.root


I/O control of code

    prex.dat


Known issues

-  Makefile does not have all dependencies correct yet
   (sometimes need to "make clean ; make")

-  all the classes are somewhat incomplete, under test

